Building.HeaderInformation: ! DOE Commercial Building Benchmark ! Primary school, new construction ! Benchmark V 1.1_3.1 ! EnergyPlus V 3.1 ! ASHRAE Standards 90.1-2004 and 62-1999 ! ! Description: Single story, primary school, 25 zones ! Classrooms, gymnasium/multipurpose room, cafeteria, kitchen ! Original model developed for the K-12 Advanced Energy Design Guide ! Form: Area = 6,871 m2 (73,959 ft2); Number of Stories = 1; Shape = "E" ! Main corridor with three wings for class rooms ! Envelope: Envelope thermal properties vary with climate according to ASHRAE Standard 90.1-2004. ! Opaque constructions: steel frame walls; built up flat roof; slab-on-grade floor ! Windows: window-to-wall ratio = 35%, ! Infiltration = 0.4 cfm/ft2 above grade wall area at 0.3 in wc (75 Pa) adjusted to 0.016 in wc (4 Pa). ! 25% of full value when ventilation system on. ! HVAC: Packaged VAV with hot water re/heat; PSZ-AC and gas furnace in gymnasium, kitchen, and cafeteria ! Economizer per 90.1-2004 ! Exhaust: restroom exhaust = 300 L/s (600 cfm); Kitchen exhaust 2360 L/s (5000 cfm), 96% make up air from cafeteria ! Kitchen exhaust fan modeled as an external load to avoid getting douible the make-up air ! Refrigeration: Walk-in cooler and walk-in freezer ! ! Int. gains: W/m2 (W/ft2) lights elec plug gas plug !
